# {{ project_name }} - AIO Sandbox Deployment

Production-ready [AIO Sandbox](https://github.com/agent-infra/sandbox) deployment using Docker Compose on DigitalOcean droplets. Provides AI agents with browser, shell, filesystem, VSCode, Jupyter, and MCP servers in a single container.

